(1, 'Stunning Coastal Views and Peaceful Escape', 'Point Dume in Malibu is a breathtaking spot that offers stunning ocean views, rugged cliffs, and a serene atmosphere. The short hike to the top is well worth it, rewarding you with panoramic vistas of the Pacific, dolphins, and even migrating whales during the season. The beach below is perfect for a peaceful stroll or sunbathing away from crowds. Whether you''re into hiking, photography, or just relaxing by the sea, Point Dume is a must-visit gem along the California coast!', '2023-06-15', ST_PointFromText('POINT(34.001297776493786 -118.80645701320736)', 4326), 'Cliffside Dr &, Birdview Ave, Malibu, CA 90265', 'ChIJCVaxHgQZ6IARtqUavCkgOSM', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a8/View_north_from_Point_Dume_State_Beach.jpg/1280px-View_north_from_Point_Dume_State_Beach.jpg', 199, 954, 9, '2023-06-18 21:41:05.5320000', NULL, NULL),
(2, 'A Must-Visit for Art and Architecture Lovers', 'The Getty Center in Los Angeles is an incredible blend of art, architecture, and breathtaking views. The museum houses an impressive collection of paintings, sculptures, and decorative arts, with masterpieces from Van Gogh, Monet, and Rembrandt. The modern architecture and beautifully landscaped gardens add to the experience. The hilltop location provides stunning panoramic views of the city. Best of all, admission is free. Whether you''re an art enthusiast or just looking for a unique cultural experience, the Getty Center is a must-visit.', '2024-10-21', ST_PointFromText('POINT(34.07739637188053 -118.47327143111012)', 4326), '1200 Getty Center Dr, Los Angeles, CA 90049', 'ChIJbzYnQte8woARJaqqFVpKeNo', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/26/Getty_Center_patio.jpg/1280px-Getty_Center_patio.jpg', 235, 1097, 4, '2024-11-05 11:21:05.040000', NULL, NULL),
(3, 'A Fun and Educational Experience for All Ages', 'The Los Angeles Zoo is a great place to explore wildlife and enjoy a day surrounded by nature. Home to a diverse range of animals, from majestic lions to playful primates, the zoo offers well-maintained exhibits and informative displays. The botanical gardens add an extra touch of beauty, and the layout makes it easy to navigate. While some areas can get crowded, it’s a fantastic spot for families, animal lovers, and anyone looking for an enjoyable and educational experience in LA.', '2024-05-26', ST_PointFromText('POINT(34.14904672627733 -118.28826874228422)', 4326), '5333 Zoo Dr, Los Angeles, CA 90027', 'ChIJ1cdRl2XAwoAR_WUoKRXLQTY', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/eb/Jaguaratthezoo.jpg/1129px-Jaguaratthezoo.jpg', 5, 23, 5, '2024-06-10 01:31:25.000000', NULL, NULL),
(4, 'Breathtaking Scenic Drive and Outdoor Adventure', 'Angeles Crest Highway offers one of the most stunning scenic drives in Los Angeles, winding through the San Gabriel Mountains with breathtaking views at every turn. Whether you''re into hiking, camping, or simply enjoying a peaceful escape from the city, this route has something for everyone. There are plenty of trails, picnic spots, and overlooks to stop and take in the beauty. The air is fresh, the roads are well-maintained, and during winter, you might even see snow. A must-visit for nature lovers and adventure seekers.', '2025-02-27', ST_PointFromText('POINT(34.26464271746633 -118.174113929381)', 4326), '701 Angeles Crest Scenic Bywy, Tujunga, CA 91042', 'ChIJLXxIxf7pwoARdmE__Amp6eo', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b3/Angeles_Crest_Highway_2019.jpg/1280px-Angeles_Crest_Highway_2019.jpg', 1, 5, 3, '2025-03-01 13:26:13.000000', NULL, NULL),
(5, 'Historic Park with Urban Energy', 'MacArthur Park in Los Angeles is a unique blend of history, culture, and city life. The park features a large lake, walking paths, and plenty of green space for relaxation. It has a rich history and has long been a gathering place for the local community. While the area can be busy and somewhat gritty, it offers a glimpse into LA’s diverse urban culture. Street vendors, musicians, and public art add to its character. It’s worth a visit for those interested in the city’s history and vibrant local scene.', '2024-12-20', ST_PointFromText('POINT(34.05943707945064 -118.27710002214133)', 4326), '2230 W 6th St, Los Angeles, CA 90057', 'ChIJ96JdGuAzw4AR5ltZ-RCykY8', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/09/MacArthur_Park_soccer_fields_from_west_2015-10-18.jpg/1280px-MacArthur_Park_soccer_fields_from_west_2015-10-18.jpg', 12, 34, 5, '2024-12-23 09:42:02.000000', NULL, NULL),
(6, 'A Peaceful Retreat in the Heart of Brooklyn', 'Prospect Park is a true urban oasis, offering a perfect escape from the hustle and bustle of New York City. Designed by the same minds behind Central Park, it features scenic walking trails, open meadows, and a beautiful lake. The park is great for picnics, jogging, biking, and even boating. Highlights include the Brooklyn Botanic Garden, the Prospect Park Zoo, and the historic Boathouse. Whether you''re looking for relaxation or outdoor activities, Prospect Park is a must-visit gem in Brooklyn.', '2024-05-17', ST_PointFromText('POINT(40.66020370011474 -73.9689558161134)', 4326), 'Brooklyn, NY', 'ChIJQwRohxBbwokRmHrfAMb3ixc', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Prospect_Park_New_York_October_2015_003.jpg/1280px-Prospect_Park_New_York_October_2015_003.jpg', 57, 234, 7, '2024-12-18 21:51:05.000000', '2024-12-18 23:51:05.000000', NULL),
(7, 'A Fascinating Journey Through NYC''s Transit History', 'The New York Transit Museum is a hidden gem that takes visitors on a deep dive into the city’s transportation history. Located in a decommissioned subway station, the museum features vintage subway cars, old turnstiles, and exhibits that showcase how the transit system evolved over the decades. It’s an interactive and engaging experience, perfect for history buffs, train enthusiasts, and families alike. Walking through the old subway cars feels like stepping back in time. If you love NYC’s rich history, this museum is well worth a visit.', '2024-08-23', ST_PointFromText('POINT(40.69056949160742 -73.99006782167962)', 4326), '99 Schermerhorn St, Brooklyn, NY 11201', 'ChIJdThqNVVawokRFk58UQOvtuM', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5b/Vintage_Fleet_BRT_Brooklyn_Union_Elevated_Car_1407.jpg/1280px-Vintage_Fleet_BRT_Brooklyn_Union_Elevated_Car_1407.jpg', 12, 38, 10, '2024-09-01 21:51:05.000000', NULL, NULL),
(8, 'ა მდეე.აიღარეარნԳფკԿ:ხნხნჟსცარმლაოდ', 'მ̶͎̮͖̮̗̯̌̆̆̇̔̑͠ა̶̛̹͚̱ ̴͚̿̋̍̊̃̚ფ̷̥͕̱͖͆̋̿̂̓͛̕რ̸̡̺̦͖͍̰͑̃̈͐̓͘͜ს̷̛̞͌̓̌͌̌͆ა̵̣̲̪͍̉̀̕̚ზ̴̣̞̟̇̇͂͗ი̶̨̛̦̱͚̩̆̔̃̀̎͌ ̵̳̤̹͇̟̙̻̄͋̿̄ე̶̨͎̥͓̺̬͓̂̈́͑̄ვ̶̙̼̮̻̙͔̔̎̚ͅლ̸̰͖͙̠͎͓̃̎ზ̵͖̑́͆̃̈́͋ა̷͇̯̥̞͍̌͜ე̶̱̈́̎ყ̴͓̲̙͑̀̈́͋̓̃͜ ̴̛̙͕̹̻̉̕̚͘ე̸̺̰͍͛̆͜დ̵͉͛̌͋̒რ̶͙͙͕͇̀̂́̕͝ა🐟̵͔̗͇̱̽͆̒̿ͅ ̷̝̈́ც̴̞͓̭̮̜͛̀̓̓̐̓͝ლ̷͇̘̈̾̄͛̏̀͒ი̶̛̹͔̌̋ი̷̢̯̜̱͐ნ̷̧̛́͒ͅო̶̞͙̜̻̤͉̘͊ბ̸̯̜̞̏̋̿̕͘͝ ̴̧͍͖͘ნ̸̬͈̼̗͔̦̪̒̿̎ა̴̥̏̀ა̷͈̥͈̲̭̪̉̉͐ო̴͉̹̞̪̑̈́̇̄̕მ̴̝̝̝͑͝ე̷͈̟̟̲́̐ჩ̴̙̅́͒̓̇გ̵̧͇̘̮̹̰̀͝ 😭', '2024-11-30', ST_PointFromText('POINT(26.744784 -42.643880)', 4326), 'Atlantis', NULL, 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/db/Underwater_archaeology.jpg', 0, 0, 1, '2024-12-01 02:38:38.000000', NULL, NULL),
(9, 'Intimate French Dining in Greenwich Village', 'MIMI is a cozy French bistro nestled in New York City''s Greenwich Village. The restaurant offers a charming ambiance reminiscent of classic Parisian eateries. The menu features traditional French dishes with a modern twist, such as the notable Riz Noir—a black squid ink risotto topped with grilled squid and shavings of bottarga. The roast chicken is also a reliable choice, known for its moist and flavorful preparation. While the space is intimate, which can lead to a bustling atmosphere, the attentive service and culinary delights make it a worthwhile dining experience for those seeking authentic French cuisine in the heart of Manhattan.', '2024-07-24', ST_PointFromText('POINT(40.72837218315401 -74.0006565061417)', 4326), '185 Sullivan St, New York, NY 10012', 'ChIJQW1zApJZwokRKDxrWkdKo5c', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/be/Mimi_%28New_York_City_restaurant%29_%E2%80%93_January_2023_%E2%80%93_by_MainlyTwelve.jpg/1280px-Mimi_%28New_York_City_restaurant%29_%E2%80%93_January_2023_%E2%80%93_by_MainlyTwelve.jpg', 1, 5, 6, '2024-07-10 21:51:05.000000', NULL, NULL),
(10, 'A Must-See for History and Military Enthusiasts', 'The Intrepid Sea, Air & Space Museum is an unforgettable experience, offering visitors the chance to explore a real aircraft carrier, historic fighter jets, a space shuttle, and even a submarine. The interactive exhibits bring military and aviation history to life, making it a great destination for both adults and kids. Walking through the massive USS Intrepid and standing beneath the Space Shuttle Enterprise is awe-inspiring. Whether you''re passionate about history, technology, or just looking for a unique NYC attraction, this museum is well worth a visit.', '2025-02-23', ST_PointFromText('POINT(40.76490244641803 -74.00083596515348)', 4326), 'Pier 86, W 46th St, New York, NY 10036', 'ChIJnxlg1U5YwokR8T90UrZiIwI', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e6/Intrepid_Museum_%2849052290092%29.jpg/1280px-Intrepid_Museum_%2849052290092%29.jpg', 15, 72, 2, '2025-02-25 21:51:05.000000', '2025-02-25 21:51:05.000000', NULL),
(11, 'An Engaging and Family-Friendly Aquarium Experience', 'The Seattle Aquarium offers a fascinating glimpse into marine life, with exhibits showcasing the diverse ecosystem of the Pacific Northwest. Highlights include the underwater dome with 360-degree views of local sea life, playful sea otters, and the touch pools where visitors can interact with starfish and sea anemones. The aquarium is well-maintained, educational, and great for families with kids. While it’s not the largest aquarium, the engaging exhibits and friendly staff make it a worthwhile visit for anyone interested in marine conservation and ocean life.', '2025-03-01', ST_PointFromText('POINT(47.60739929597848 -122.34295649612991)', 4326), '1483 Alaskan Way Pier 59, Seattle, WA 98101', 'ChIJQ_oEiK1qkFQRg3bU4l3mmWs', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b3/The_Seattle_Aquarium%E2%80%99s_Window_on_Washington_Water_exhibit_dive_show.jpg/1280px-The_Seattle_Aquarium%E2%80%99s_Window_on_Washington_Water_exhibit_dive_show.jpg', 0, 0, 4, '2025-03-02 21:51:05.000000', NULL, NULL),
(12, 'A Lush Paradise for Nature Lovers', 'Fairchild Tropical Botanic Garden is a breathtaking escape into a world of rare and exotic plants. Located in Coral Gables, Florida, this 83-acre garden features stunning landscapes, winding pathways, and vibrant collections of tropical flora. Visitors can explore lush rainforests, serene butterfly gardens, and even a massive collection of palms and cycads. The garden is beautifully maintained, offering both relaxation and education through guided tours and seasonal events. Whether you''re a botany enthusiast or just looking for a peaceful retreat, Fairchild is a must-visit gem.', '2024-08-12', ST_PointFromText('POINT(25.67679087828212 -80.27203802454832)', 4326), 'Old Cutler Rd, Coral Gables, FL 33156', 'ChIJu_e4BnTI2YgREAOg3GxMK8g', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c7/Bailey_Palm_Glade_%285752321428%29.jpg/1280px-Bailey_Palm_Glade_%285752321428%29.jpg', 5, 19, 7, '2024-08-23 21:51:05.000000', NULL, NULL),
(13, 'Hotel Globo: Simplicidade e Aconchego em Palmelo', 'Em Palmelo, Goiás, o Hotel Globo é uma opção de hospedagem que oferece simplicidade e conforto. Classificado como o número 1 de 2 alojamentos especializados na região, o hotel é reconhecido por sua atmosfera acolhedora e atendimento atencioso. Embora as comodidades sejam básicas, a hospitalidade e a tranquilidade do local proporcionam uma estadia agradável para os visitantes que buscam descanso e contato com a natureza.', '2024-09-12', ST_PointFromText('POINT(-7.112519215251036 -34.88881569975719)', 4326), 'Largo de São Frei Pedro Gonçalves, Praça São Pedro Gonçalves, 7 - Varadouro, PB, Brazil', 'ChIJD7HJttznrAcRGsy60K2wwlQ', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ae/Hotel_Globo%2C_Jo%C3%A3o_Pessoa_%28PB%29.jpg/804px-Hotel_Globo%2C_Jo%C3%A3o_Pessoa_%28PB%29.jpg', 1, 4, 3, '2024-09-18 21:51:05.000000', NULL, NULL),
(14, 'Un Viaje al Pasado en la Cueva del Milodón', 'El Monumento Natural Cueva del Milodón, ubicado en la Patagonia chilena, es un sitio arqueológico e histórico fascinante. Esta enorme cueva es famosa por los restos fósiles del milodón, un mamífero prehistórico que habitó la región hace miles de años. Al recorrer el sendero, los visitantes pueden admirar formaciones rocosas impresionantes y una réplica del milodón en la entrada. El entorno natural es espectacular, con vistas a montañas y lagos patagónicos. Ideal para amantes de la historia y la naturaleza, es una parada imperdible cerca de Puerto Natales.', '2024-10-14', ST_PointFromText('POINT(-51.56835120302654 -72.61933729599725)', 4326), 'Y-290 8, Natales, Magallanes y la Antártica Chilena, Chile', 'ChIJlS54ehvwr70RuetuKjjANK8', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1e/Cueva_del_Milod%C3%B3n_%2839330091455%29.jpg/1243px-Cueva_del_Milod%C3%B3n_%2839330091455%29.jpg', 3, 13, 8, '2024-12-18 21:51:05.000000', NULL, NULL),
(15, '「大阪城公園: 歴史と自然が融合する美しい場所」', '大阪城公園は、歴史と自然が見事に調和した場所です。公園内には、壮大な大阪城がそびえ立ち、周囲には広大な緑地や池があります。春には桜が満開になり、花見スポットとしても有名です。城の内部は博物館として公開されており、大阪の歴史や文化について学ぶことができます。散策するにも最適な場所で、ジョギングやピクニックを楽しむ人々も多く、家族連れにもおすすめのスポットです。', '2025-01-24', ST_PointFromText('POINT(34.686479280514874 135.5262141811361)', 4326), '1-1 Osakajo, Chuo Ward, Osaka, 540-0002, Japan', 'ChIJVVVld8ngAGARi9mE-a6e9mc', 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/23/OsakaCastle-MainTower02.jpg', 5, 19, 6, '2025-02-01 11:51:05.000000', '2025-02-01 11:55:05.000000', NULL);
